These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
City: colone, rome, boston, liverpool, venice, hamburg, edinburgh
 1. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to venice##7
 3. the person traveling to rome is somewhere between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to colone##7
 4. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is not to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##8
 6. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to edinburgh##7
 9. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##8
10. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| City   | venice | colone | rome | boston | liverpool | hamburg | edinburgh |

