.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, aristoff, blend, bolivar, cain, bluemaster, bongani
 1. the bluemaster-smoker is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 2. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5
 3. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the right of the aristoff-smoker##5
 4. the aristoff-smoker is in an even position##4
 5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
 6. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the left of the aristoff-smoker##5
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 8. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 9. the bongani-smoker is in an even position##4
10. the cain-smoker is not to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| Cigar   | bolivar | aristoff | bluemaster | bongani | blend | tiparillo | cain |

