.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-3::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, manager, electrician, musician, security-guard, accountant, librarian
 1. the musician is not to the left of the accountant##8
 2. the librarian is in an even position##4
 3. the accountant is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
 4. the security-guard is on the left or right of the accountant##3
 5. the musician is on the left or right of the accountant##3
 6. the librarian is not to the right of the bartender##8
 7. the electrician is somewhere between the accountant and the manager##7
 8. the bartender is in an odd position##4
 9. the bartender is not to the right of the electrician##8
10. the accountant is on the right of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Job   | security-guard | accountant | musician | librarian | bartender | electrician | manager |

