.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-4::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, singing, puzzles, dancing, skydiving, magic-tricks, fishing
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is singing##7
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is singing##7
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is dancing##7
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |  2  |   3   |    4     |   5   |   6    |  7   |
| Hobby   | puzzles | woodworking | dancing | fishing | skydiving | singing | magic-tricks |

