 2. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person watching family movies##8
 3. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
 4. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
 5. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
 6. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
 8. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the person watching family movies##8
 9. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching satire movies##7
10. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
11. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
12. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3    |    4     |     5      |     6     |     7      |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | martial-arts | romance | family | fantasy | scientific | zombie |

